### **Business Type** Perfect for **SaaS**,**B2B**, and **E-Commerce** businesses aiming to streamline their sales and client engagement processes.

### **Template Type** Ideal for **Campaigns**,**Reports**, and **Dashboards**, this template is designed to simplify follow-ups and boost conversions.

### **Use Case** This template helps sales teams manage leads effectively by automating client engagement after quoting, ensuring opportunities are not missed.

### ** Key Features of the Flow **Automated Follow-Ups**: Keeps client engagement active with automatic follow-up actions after a quote is sent.

- **Call Scheduling**: Schedules client calls to maintain timely communication.

- ** Email Automation **: Sends personalized follow-up emails based on client interactions, saving time and adding a personal touch.

### **Steps used in creating the flow** You can **[click here](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/42360310797337-Streamline-Follow-Ups-with-Smart-Flow#)** to learn how to create a new Smart Flow or access the Flow Templates.

- **Trigger:**[Deal Stage Match](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/36768388746521-Deal-Stage-Match)**- **Description:** Triggers follow-up actions when a deal reaches the "Quotation Sent" stage.

- **Use Case:** Ensures timely engagement, helping move deals forward efficiently.

- **Interactions:** [**Wait**](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38138356545433-Wait):- **Description:** Adds a 2-day wait after "Quotation Sent" to give the client time to review the proposal.

- **Use Case:** Ensures thoughtful follow-ups without overwhelming the client.[**Branch**](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/37780627045657-Branch):- **Description:** Checks if the deal has progressed to the "Negotiation" stage and identifies the necessary actions to move forward.

- **Use Case:** Ensures sales teams take the right steps in negotiating terms, improving deal closure rates.

![mceclip0.png](./images/mceclip0-13.png)

- * Actions ***[Create Activity Record](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38098733305753-Create-Record) (Option 1)**:- **Description:** initiates a follow-up call to review the quote with the client, addressing any questions or concerns.

- **Use Case:** Ensures clients fully understand the quote and clarifies any doubts, improving the chances of closing the deal.

- **[Exit](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38138458679577-Exit-Flow) (Option 2)**:- **Description:** Ends the flow for deals that have been successfully closed and marked as won.

- **Use Case:** Streamlines the sales process by closing out deals that are finalized, reducing unnecessary follow-up actions.

- **[Create Activity Record](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38098733305753-Create-Record) (Option 3)**:- **Description:** The sales team reviews the deal’s parameters to determine if it’s ready to move into the negotiation stage.

- **Use Case:** Helps evaluate the readiness of a deal to move forward, ensuring proper preparation before entering negotiations.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### ** Breakup of Items Used in the Flow **Trigger **Deal Stage Match **: Initiates the flow when a deal reaches the "Quotation Sent" stage, ensuring timely follow-ups.

- ** Condition **Branch**: Splits the flow into different paths depending on whether the client responds, advances to negotiation, or the deal is closed.

- **Actions **Create Activity Record **: Generates tasks for follow-up calls or deal reviews to ensure timely action.

- ** Exit **: Ends the flow for deals that are successfully closed and marked as won.

- ** End** The flow concludes once the necessary follow-up actions are completed.

### ** Benefits **Efficiency**: Reduces manual work by automating repetitive follow-up tasks.

- **Enhanced Engagement**: Maintains consistent and meaningful communication with clients.

- ** Increased Conversion **: Keeps clients engaged and moves them forward in the sales pipeline, boosting the likelihood of closing deals
